			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">View source for Applying Service Locator Pattern to UE4</span></h1>
			<div id="bodyContent">
				<div id="contentSub">← <a href="/Applying_Service_Locator_Pattern_to_UE4" title="Applying Service Locator Pattern to UE4">Applying Service Locator Pattern to UE4</a></div>
																<div id="mw-content-text"><p>You do not have permission to edit this page, for the following reason:
</p>
<div class="permissions-errors">
